WEBVTT

00:00:01.802 --> 00:00:05.126
Today I want to confess something to you,

00:00:05.150 --> 00:00:08.045
but first of all I'm going to ask you
a couple of questions.

00:00:08.069 --> 00:00:09.822
How many people here have children?

00:00:11.676 --> 00:00:13.254
And how many of you are confident

00:00:13.278 --> 00:00:15.332
that you know how
to bring up your children

00:00:15.356 --> 00:00:16.591
in exactly the right way?

00:00:16.615 --> 00:00:20.056
(Laughter)

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:23.219
OK, I don't see too many hands
going up on that second one,

00:00:23.243 --> 00:00:24.790
and that's my confession, too.

00:00:24.814 --> 00:00:26.065
I've got three boys;

00:00:26.089 --> 00:00:27.896
they're three, nine and 12.

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.986
